Barroso Wants to Lead by Example on Financial Transaction Tax

-- B y   P a t r i c k   H e n r y
-- 
2011-10-23T14:57:27Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-10-23/barroso-wants-to-lead-by-example-on-financial-transaction-tax.html
European Commission President  Jose
Barroso  said  Europe  should lead by example on implementing a
financial transactions tax. He spoke to reporters after a
European Union summit in Brussels today.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
